</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col2" namest="col2" nameend="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Media type 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">If the media type encoded into the .print file is not supported by the controller, a warning message displays: 
</p></li></ul><fig id="GUID-752CE914-2B8A-4781-8914-944E93BC4AE8" class="- topic/fig "><desc class="- topic/desc "><p class="- topic/p ">Example warning 
</p></desc><image href="GUID-35ACDD02-180F-4715-8C29-353C64047EC1-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-35ACDD02-180F-4715-8C29-353C64047EC1-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">6 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" namest="col2" nameend="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Select a media type (*) from the Media type drop down list (or, select Same as file if you want to submit the job without changing the media type selected within the job header): 
</p><fig id="GUID-C51B0217-13DC-4A5D-83CF-88131ADFF6EC" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-FF4BE4DA-8682-43B0-B73F-DC3631BCD9A7-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-FF4BE4DA-8682-43B0-B73F-DC3631BCD9A7-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p ">(*): Use media equal or close to the media type information you collected from the customer 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">7 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" namest="col2" nameend="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Click Submit 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">The pop-up window will disappear when the job has been transmitted fully. 
</p></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="GUID-61044B86-68E0-4EF8-94A3-300AB350E167" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Additional information</title><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Do NOT click on “Submit” several times if nothing seems to happen: these actions are memorized and will cause several job submissions (as many times as the Submit button was clicked). 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Do NOT click in the command window (‘socketsubmitter’, mentioning “Sending: _tmp.print”) when it displays otherwise it will stop the file submission. 
</p></li></ol></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-5C937DF0-2BDD-497B-B1AC-3013A8804D24.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Diagnostics</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
